        <p>Hausfeld &amp; Co is registered as a data controller in the Data Protection Register of the UK Information Commissioner&rsquo;s Office under registration number Z1953172.&nbsp;A copy of our data privacy policy is&nbsp;<a href="https://www.hausfeld.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">available here</a>.&nbsp;The Information Commissioner&rsquo;s Office can be contacted via its website https://ico.org.uk or by telephone on 0044 (0)303 123 1113.</p>

